  "mainText": "Italiano English Reserved Area Contacts Company Pens Customisation Sample kits Finishes Recycled pens More maxema ® via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com P PRODUCTS Our pens Kind / Kind / Icon Pure / Flow Pure / Dot / Zink / Pixel / Bay / Mood Metal / Kind / Mood / Flow / View / Tag Green / Next / Tag / Icon / Icon green / Ethic Search by color rose/purple azure / blue green yellow/orange red cream/brown grey black white select a color S Services customisation packaging pantone colors sample kits C COMPANY Maxema Company contacts FAVORITES SAMPLE KITS ACCOUNT FAQ MEDIA DISCLAIMER As you like it, as you are Customisation Imprint your brand Once assembled, the pen is ready to be “dressed” with a brand or message, choosing the most suitable combinations between finishes, colors and printing techniques. At the end of the process, the pen is finally ready to bring its precious message: your image. Pad printing Screen printing Laser engraving Hover over the image to enlarge it Side Front Side Front Front High quality printing The printing, pad printing or screen printing takes place with the use of high-hold paints, while laser engraving allows even metallic parts to be customised. Packaging Our My Case and My Box cases have been designed to enhance the product and best convey your message. Customisable on multi sides with high-quality pad printing, they are ideal promotional tools for fairs, press kits or gift sets. Technical informations Discover more Refill Our refills were created to give your pen the stroke you prefer.The tube is made of polypropylene and the inks are non-toxic and safe, compliant with the European regulation REACH and the American regulation TSCA. X-20 · tungsten carbide ball Ø 1 mm · lenght 107 mm · for up to 2000 meters of writing Jumbo · tungsten carbide ball Ø 1 mm · lenght 107 mm · for up to 2500 meters of writing RT 90 Parker Type Black Tube, Branded with M